Once there was a monkey who lived in a tree.A crocodile came by one day and the monkey greeted him and they got chatting.Soon the two became inseparable friends.The mokey used to feed the crocodile
fruits every day.This was well liked by the crocodile.He also started gifting the monkey little things like special bananas which he found on his way.Not a day passed by when the monkey had not met the crocodile.The crocodile started talking about the monkey to his wife.
